Package: logdriver
Type: Package
Title: Easy Cloud-Hosted Logging for Small Projects
Version: 0.1.1.9000
Author: Christopher Belanger
Maintainer: Christopher Belanger <christopher@belangeranalytics.com>
Description: Logdriver is a simple free log-management tool for small projects.
    It consists of this R package and an accompanying web app. The 
    package makes it easy to send log information to the web app, and 
    the app can be hosted in the cloud to store and analyze logs. The R package
    can also be used locally to write structured log entries to stdout.
